An economic evaluation of contingency management for completion of hepatitis B 
vaccination in those on treatment for opiate dependence.

Rafia R(1), Dodd PJ(1), Brennan A(1), Meier PS(2), Hope VD(3), Ncube F(3), 
Byford S(4), Tie H(4), Metrebian N(5), Hellier J(6), Weaver T(7), Strang J(5).

