In this part of the series we explain the detailed literature review and the 
calculations of impacts and damage costs of mercury and lead. Methodology and 
general assumptions are explained in the companion article, Part 1 of this 
series, and the spreadsheet with the calculations is available as a 
supplementary file of Part 1.3 For mercury, the damage cost is 22,937 €2013 /kg 
