to mortality from heart disease, the rest from loss of IQ points. For lead, the 
damage cost is 29,343 €2013 /kg, about 80% due to mortality and 20% due to IQ 
loss; there does not seem to be a no-effect threshold. These costs are per kg of 
emitted pollutant.

